Privacy Policy

First Responders Africa respects your privacy and is committed to ensuring that your personal information remains secure. This privacy policy outlines how we handle any information collected or used by First Responders Africa.

Information Collection:

The app may request access to your device's location when you request emergency help. This data is only used to assist in connecting you with nearby responders and is not stored or shared.We do not collect any personal data, 
browsing history, or personally identifiable information from users during the use of the application.

Usage of Information:

Since we do not collect any user data, we do not utilize, sell, or share any information with third parties.


Changes to this Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to update or change our privacy policy at any time. Any modifications will be effective immediately upon posting the updated policy on this page.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at sidney@softifysolutionsgroup.com
